data.name: InternalServerError
data.value: The server failed to process the request.

data.name: FaultGenericError
data.value: Internal server error. The server failed to process the request with fault code {0}.

data.name: FaultLicenseExpired
data.value: The trial period for this product has expired.
data.comment: {@PseudoOK@} The message shown in the UI pages when the timebomb has expired.

data.name: FaultAccessDenied
data.value: Visio Services was unable to load this Web Drawing because the Web Drawing URL web part setting does not refer to an existing .VDW file or you do not have permissions to view it. To resolve this issue, verify that the Web Drawing URL refers to an existing .VDW file that you have permissions to view.

data.name: FaultRecalcTimedOut
data.value: Visio Services was unable to load this Web Drawing because it is either too large or too complex. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to increase the amount of time Visio Services may process this Web Drawing or decrease the complexity of this Web Drawing using Visio.

data.name: FaultDataConnectivityError
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because an underlying data source is unreachable. To resolve this issue, try again or ask your system administrator to make sure that all underlying data sources are available and reachable.

data.name: FaultOfficeDataConnectionFileNotFound
data.value: Visio Services was unable to update external data connections in this Web Drawing because it could not retrieve an underlying data connection file. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to verify that the data connection file exists and verify that the path to the data connection file embedded in this Web Drawing is correct.

data.name: FaultOfficeDataConnectionFileRetrievalError
data.value: Visio Services was unable to update external data connections in this Web Drawing because it could not retrieve an underlying data connection file. To resolve this issue, contact your system administrator.

data.name: FaultOfficeDataConnectionFileAccessDenied
data.value: Visio Services was unable to update external data connections in this Web Drawing because you do not have permissions to access an underlying data connection file, or this file does not exist. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to verify that the relevant data connection file exists and to grant you permissions to access it.

data.name: FaultIncompatibleDomain
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because an underlying data connection attempted to retrieve data from a SharePoint list hosted on a domain you do not have access to. To resolve this issue, update this Web Drawing to contain only connections to SharePoint lists within this domain or ask your system administrator to grant you access to other domains.
data.comment: Error message displayed in browser when a diagram is connected to a SharePoint list from a different domain to which the user has no access.

data.name: FaultWssListAccessDenied
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because you do not have permissions to access an underlying SharePoint list data source. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to grant you permissions to access this data source.
data.comment: Error message displayed in browser when a diagram is connected to a SharePoint list which the user has no access.

data.name: FaultWssViewAccessDenied
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because a connection to an underlying SharePoint list view data source failed with errors. To resolve this issue, ensure that the view is not a Personal View owned by another user, that the view exists and that you have permissions to access it.
data.comment: Error message displayed in browser when a diagram is connected to a SharePoint list view.

data.name: FaultInvalidPageNumber
data.value: Visio Services was unable to display the requested page because it does not exist within this Web Drawing. To resolve this issue, make sure to request a page that exists within this Web Drawing.

data.name: FaultInvalidFileUrl
data.value: Visio Services was unable to load this Web Drawing because the Web Drawing URL web part setting is invalid. To resolve this issue, verify that the Web Drawing URL is properly formed and refers to an existing .VDW file.

data.name: FaultRasterizationError
data.value: Visio Services was unable to display the requested page because of an error during Web Drawing rasterization. To resolve this issue, install Silverlight or contact your system administrator.

data.name: FaultEmptyServerData
data.value: Visio Services was unable to load this Web Drawing because its file format is unsupported or this Web Drawing may be corrupt. To resolve this issue, save this Web Drawing from Visio as a valid .VDW file.

data.name: FaultOpenServerFileFailed
data.value: Visio Services was unable to load this Web Drawing because its file format is unsupported or this Web Drawing may be corrupt. To resolve this issue, save this Web Drawing from Visio as a valid .VDW file.

data.name: FaultNoReadPermissionToFile
data.value: Visio Services was unable to load this Web Drawing because you do not have the permissions to view it. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to grant you permissions to view it.
data.comment: An error message through browser when the above happens

data.name: FaultFileLocationNotTrusted
data.value: The server does not trust the location of the specified Visio file.

data.name: FaultExceededMaxDiagramSize
data.value: Visio Services was unable to load this Web Drawing because it is larger than the maximum Web Drawing size it is allowed to open and process. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to increase the maximum Web Drawing size Visio Services can process.
data.comment: Error message shown in the user interface / logs when the Visio file size is more than what the administrator configured it to be

data.name: QuotaExceededExceptionMessage
data.value: Internal server error. The requested Web Drawing is too large to render.
data.comment: Error message shown in the user interface / logs when the generated Visio file size is more what the system supports.

data.name: FaultIncompatibleVersion
data.value: Visio Services was unable to load this Web Drawing because it was created with an older version of Visio. To resolve this issue, open this Web drawing with an updated version of Visio and save it again.

data.name: FaultDataProviderNotTrusted
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because one or more data provider required by these connections is not trusted by the Visio Graphics Service. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to add the data providers you need to refresh this Web Drawing to the Trusted Data Providers list of the Visio Graphics Service.

data.name: FaultDataBindingConflict
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because changes have been made to the structure of an underlying data source since this Web Drawing was last saved. To resolve this issue, restore the data source structure to its previous state or update the data connection information in this Web Drawing using Visio.

data.name: FaultUnableToGetExternalDataSourceCredentials
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because it was unable to retrieve credentials to access underlying data sources from the farm's Secure Store Service. To resolve this issue, contact your system administrator.
data.comment: Shown in webpart when the Secure Store service does not return credentials

data.name: FaultUnattendedAccountTypeMismatch
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections because the Unattended Service Account provided by the service administrator is not of type Windows. To resolve this issue, contact your system administrator.
data.comment: Shown in webpart when the Secure Store service does not return credentials of type windows for the Unattended Service Account

data.name: ConflictColumnDeleted
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because of changes in the structure of an underlying data source. One or more columns in this data source have been deleted after this Web Drawing was last saved. To resolve this issue, restore the deleted columns or update the data connection information in this Web Drawing using Visio.

data.name: ConflictColumnTypeChanged
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because of changes in the structure of an underlying data source. One or more columns in this data source have changed data type after this Web Drawing was last saved. To resolve this issue, restore the data types of the affected columns to their previous values or update the data connection information in this Web drawing using Visio.

data.name: ConflictRowDeleted
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because of changes in the structure of an underlying data source. One or more rows in this data source have been deleted after this Web Drawing was last saved. To resolve this issue, restore the deleted rows or update the data connection information in this Web Drawing using Visio.

data.name: ConflictRowDuplicated
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because of changes in the structure of an underlying data source. One or more rows with duplicate primary keys have been introduced into this data source after this Web Drawing was last saved. To resolve this issue, delete primary key duplicates or update the data connection information in this Web Drawing using Visio.

data.name: ConflictPrimaryKeyColumnDeleted
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because of changes in the structure of an underlying data source. The primary key column in this data source has been deleted after this Web Drawing was last saved. To resolve this issue, restore the deleted primary key column or update the data connection information in this Webd Drawing using Visio.

data.name: AddonDataHandlerTimeoutError
data.value: Visio Services was unable to update external data connections in this Web Drawing because a connection to an underlying custom data source timed out. To resolve this issue, try again or contact your system administrator.

data.name: ExternalDataRefreshFailed
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because a connection to an underlying Excel file data source failed to refresh. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to verify that Excel Services are enabled on this site and are functioning properly.

data.name: ExcelServicesFailed
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because a connection to an underlying Excel file data source failed with errors. To resolve this issue, ask your system administrator to verify that Excel Services are enabled on this site and are functioning properly.

data.name: IncompatibleDomainForExcelFile
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because it contains a connection to an underlying Excel file data source that is hosted in a domain you do not have access to. To resolve this issue, update this Web Drawing with connections to an Excel file within this domain or ask your system administrator to grant you access to other domains.

data.name: ExcelFileOpenNotFound
data.value: Visio Services was unable to refresh external data connections in this Web Drawing because an underlying Excel file data source was not found. To resolve this issue ensure that the Excel file exists at the specified location.

However, increasing this value means that users will not see their Web Drawings refreshing as frequently.
